---
title: One-Pan Chicken, Chorizo & Cherry Tomato Risoni for Dinner with Chicken, Chorizo & Creamy Pesto Wraps for Lunch
description: Cook once, with a twist for lunch. Cook an amazing dinner as usual, then put a new spin on the recipe to create something different for lunch the next day! Chicken and chorizo are on double duty tonight, in a satisfying bowl of risoni for dinner and wraps with pesto for lunch tomorrow. Extra delicious!

